nodes.text: Puwanini, nicknamed Puwan, was a female individual who worked for the Scrapper Guild on Bracca after joining around a year before the First Order/Resistance War. She was the sister of Pacer Agoyo, a recruit of the Resistance who was part of a team sent to Bracca to recover scrapped starships. Puwanini and a number of guild employees assisted the Resistance team in their mission.
